Translate Professional 4.20 for iPhone and iPad Presenting: Dictionary lookup for some words New copy functionality. Tap the text to show the menu. Tap a word to highlight it in the Single Translation view. If a definition is available a button will appear. Mark your favorite translations and access them from the Library! Full screen mode for translations. Simply tap the arrows! Slight graphics changes all over the app. IMPORTANT: If you ever have any problem at all with the voices simply download them again for a fresh updated voice For free of course! . This will upgrade the voice to a newer better version. Remember if you have any questions at all simply contact us through: facebook.com traduko Twitter: valross2 News for developers New URL scheme! Translate Professional now responds to the translatepro: URL scheme Examples: Launch app: translatepro: Launch paste from clipboard: translatepro: clipboard Launch and paste the text into the translation field: translatepro: text TEXT

Translate Professional 4.1 for iPhone and iPad Presenting: JAPANESE and CHINESE voices and a new icon! New stunning beautiful icon. Complete support for the new iPad retina screens! IMPORTANT: If you have any problem at all with the voices simply download them again for a fresh updated voice For free of course! . This will upgrade the voice to a newer better version.
